data.description: This precious charmer is just right.  Just the right size if your starting out, starting over or just want a change.  The Semi-Open floor plan allows for that together feeling.  The large master bedroom has plenty of space to move and hold even the largest furnishings.  Laundry room has plenty of space for those large washers and dryers.  There is also a separate area for a freezer or even turn it into a pantry.  Like to sit outside and sip that morning coffee?  The large covered deck is perfect for that.  Spacious back yard is fully fenced for the kids, or even the fur kids.  Perfect place to put your own charm on and be at home.
